Package: glances
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, libstatgrab6, python-statgrab (>=0.5)
Description: CLI curses based monitoring tool
 Glances is a CLI curses based monitoring tool for GNU/Linux or BSD OS.
 Glances uses the libstatgrab library to get information from your system.
 .
 It monitors CPU, load, memory, network bandwidth, disk I/O, disk use, process.
